transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Haan ji mam meri baat ho gayi hai Ritesh sir se.
Customer: Hello
Executive: Haan haan hello.
Executive: Haan ji mam meri baat ho gayi hai main paral bol rahi hu mam.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: To meri sari baat ho gayi hai Ritesh sir se unka koi concern nahi tha mam actually wo na koi catalog vagera update kar rahe the to by default unse call lag gayi thi.
Executive: To ab main na mam yahan se concern close kar rahi hu aap ek bari unko boliyega unke pass ek mail jayega to usme wo satisfied feed fill kar denge theek hai mam.
Customer: Achcha feedback ke liye.
Executive: Wo haan mam wo mera feedback rahega theek hai.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: And mam agar aapko koi problem hai like abhi kuch cheeze nahi samajh mein aayi to aap mujhe bata sakte ho main abhi bhi aapko guide kar sakti hu.
Customer: Haan mam abhi thoda to free nahi hu main thodi der se lagati hu.
Executive: Theek hai mam jab aap free ho jaiyega tab mujhe call kar lijiyega baki main abhi concern wala close kar deti hu.
Customer: Theek hai mam.
Executive: Okay. Okay mam aap feedback ke liye aap unko bol dijiyega ki yes kar de.
Customer: Haan haan theek hai.
Executive: Okay.
Customer: Ji ab main aapko discussion kar deti hu.
